01:54:10,543 --> 01:54:12,420
It was a long time ago.

1408
01:54:14,080 --> 01:54:15,251
Where have you been?

1409
01:54:16,682 --> 01:54:20,629
I been working.
Working, traveling.

1410
01:54:20,753 --> 01:54:24,257
I think I've been halfway around
the world since I last saw Doris.

1411
01:54:26,459 --> 01:54:28,132
How old is she now?

1412
01:54:28,260 --> 01:54:30,263
Doris is 23.

1413
01:54:32,197 --> 01:54:34,040
'Cause I wanted to know.

1414
01:54:36,268 --> 01:54:38,714
You know, she was...

1415
01:54:39,905 --> 01:54:41,748
She was too young when I...

1416
01:54:44,477 --> 01:54:46,616
Well, she's happy,
and that's good.

1417
01:54:49,882 --> 01:54:51,418
I'll tell her you came to see me.

1418
01:54:51,549 --> 01:54:53,723
Ah, that's not gonna matter.

1419
01:54:54,820 --> 01:54:56,458
Give me a break.

1420
01:55:03,562 --> 01:55:05,337
It was nice to see you.

1421
01:55:06,432 --> 01:55:08,105
Am I leaving?

1422
01:55:09,768 --> 01:55:12,875
