You can come in.

1423
01:55:13,004 --> 01:55:17,384
- Nah. I gotta go.
- OK.

1424
01:55:17,509 --> 01:55:19,717
Thank you.

1425
01:55:19,844 --> 01:55:23,816
- How's Mr. Solstad?
- Why, he's very good.

1426
01:55:23,949 --> 01:55:26,827
He's working, and...

1427
01:55:26,951 --> 01:55:29,455
- Will you tell him I said hello?
- All right.

1428
01:55:33,526 --> 01:55:37,406
So, her name is Doris Day?
Like the Doris Day?

1429
01:55:37,530 --> 01:55:38,668
Yes.

1430
01:55:38,998 --> 01:55:42,036
- The movie star.
- Yes.

1431
01:55:45,708 --> 01:55:47,380
<font color="#808080">BOY:</font><i> Who are you?</i>

1432
01:55:47,509 --> 01:55:49,510
<font color="#808080">BOY 2:</font> <i> My name is Casper.</i>

1433
01:55:49,644 --> 01:55:53,023
<font color="#808080">BOY:</font><i> Hey, Casper.
Would you like to play pirate with me?</i>

1434
01:55:53,147 --> 01:55:57,254
<font color="#808080">CASPER:</font><i> Oh, boy! Would I!</i>

1435
01:55:57,385 --> 01:56:00,026
<font color="#808080">BOY:</font><i> How are we gonna
