1441
01:56:26,147 --> 01:56:29,094
<i>We're tied together.</i>

1442
01:56:29,218 --> 01:56:31,289
<i>Who got to you, Freddie?</i>

1443
01:56:31,420 --> 01:56:34,799
<i>- What?
- Who got to you?</i>

1444
01:56:34,923 --> 01:56:36,664
Nobody.

1445
01:56:38,527 --> 01:56:41,769
<i>Come to England.
You'll love it here.</i>

1446
01:56:41,897 --> 01:56:44,878
<i>Andi think it'll do you some good.
Can you do it?</i>

1447
01:56:45,000 --> 01:56:50,415
<i>- Where?
- We have a new school. It's in England.</i>

1448
01:56:50,539 --> 01:56:52,643
Well, my spaceship's in the shop.

1449
01:56:52,775 --> 01:56:55,779
<font color="#D900D9">(CHUCKLING)</font><i>
You've still got it.</i>

1450
01:56:55,911 --> 01:56:58,049
<i>Would you bring me some Kools?</i>

1451
01:56:58,179 --> 01:56:59,955
They don't have them there?

1452
01:57:00,081 --> 01:57:03,029
<i>The only bad pan'
over here, no Kools.</i>

1453
01:57:06,888 --> 01:57:08,266
How'd you find me?

1454
01:57:08,389 --> 01:57:11,893
<i>Freddie, I have a matter
of such urgency,</i>

1455
01:57:12,027 --> 01:57:14,563
<i>a matter that only you
can help me with.</i>

1456
01:57:14,696 --> 01:57:18,337
<i>That may, in fact, cure
the insane once and for all.</i>

1457
01:57:18,467 --> 01:57:20,571
<i>I can cure you.</i>

1458
01:57:20,701 --> 01:57:22,739
<i>And I remember where we've met.</i>

1459
01:57:22,870 --> 01:57:27,250
<i>- Come to England. I'll tell you.
<font color="#D900D9">(LINE DISCONNECTS)</font></i>

1460
01:57:27,375 --> 01:57:30,822
<font color="#808080">BOY:</font><i> Now, for the treasure!</i>

1461
01:57:30,946 --> 01:57:35,053
<i>"X" marks the spot
where the sunken treasure is.</i>

1462
01:57:37,952 --> 01:57:40,365
<font color="#808080">CASPER:</font><i>
Golly, Billy, there's the "X."</i>

1463
01:57:40,489 --> 01:57:42,934
<font color="#808080">BILLY:</font><i>
I'll get the treasure, Casper.</i>

1464
01:57:43,058 --> 01:57:47,404
<font color="#808080">CASPER:</font><i> The captain never
